GO TEST SERVER:

It is basically a go server where you tst some APIs like /health, /name like that.
and Our mainly use of this server to build a dockerfile or multisatge dockerfile where we can optimize the size of an image. and after that we are going to build a workflow where
we ust trigger the worflow if any one just push any changes to repo. 

How to run locally :
